        objectClick3(destinationID, destinationX, destinationY);
        break;

    case 3816:
        TheifStall("scimitar stall", "and recieve 50k WEWT.", 1,
                100 * playerLevel[12], 995, 50000, 30, 0x340);
        break;

    case 4874:
        TheifStall("scimitar stall", "and recieve a chisel.", 1,
                100 * playerLevel[17], 1755, 1, 30, 0x340);
        break;
